# SDLC Skills — DevOps/SRE

## Your Skills (14)

### Deployment & Release
- `/release-readiness-checker vX.Y.Z` — Pre-release go/no-go verdict
- `/rollback-assessor HEAD~3` — Evaluate rollback safety (GO/NO-GO)
- `/dependency-update --fix-security` — Fix vulnerable dependencies

### Incident Management
- `/incident-detector scan` — Correlate deployments with error signals
- `/incident-triager '<description>'` — Triage report with root cause candidates
- `/incident-postmortem-synthesizer recent` — Surface recurring incident patterns

### Platform Governance
- `/approval-workflow-auditor full` — Audit branch policies and pipeline gates
- `/cross-repo-standards-enforcer full` — Audit repo against org standards
- `/slo-sla-tracker full` — Track SLOs, DORA metrics, error budgets
- `/pipeline-monitor scan --all` — Detect stuck tasks and pipeline anomalies

### Security & Compliance
- `/security-audit src/` — Security vulnerability scan
- `/migration-tracker status` — Track migration progress
- `/report-trends dashboard` — Health dashboard with trends
- `/risk-tracker scan --all --escalate` — Risk register with escalation

## Your Pipelines (3)

### Deploy & Verify
Post-deployment health check:
```
/run-pipeline devops-sre/deploy-verify vX.Y.Z
```
Chain: release-readiness-checker → incident-detector → slo-sla-tracker

### Incident Response
Incident detection through remediation:
```
/run-pipeline devops-sre/incident-response 'API 500 errors since 14:30'
```
Chain: incident-detector → incident-triager → rollback-assessor

### Platform Health
Platform governance audit:
```
/run-pipeline devops-sre/platform-health
```
Chain: slo-sla-tracker → approval-workflow-auditor → cross-repo-standards-enforcer
